spec_data.Name: nodejs-https-proxy-agent
spec_data.Description:
This module provides an `http.Agent` implementation that connects to a
specified HTTP or HTTPS proxy server, and can be used with the built-in
`https` module.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 03:01:55 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: An HTTP(s) proxy http.Agent implementation for HTTPS
